HEADWORD: Sulphurize
<hw>Sul"phur*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>To combine or impregnate with sulphur or any of its compounds;
<as>as, to <ex>sulphurize</ex> caoutchouc in vulcanizing</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

